More about Amnesty International

You have the power to stop injustice. By becoming a member of=20
Amnesty International Australia for $55 a year, you strengthen our=20
voice to speak out against human rights abuses. You'll also receive=20
a copy of our quarterly Human Rights Defender magazine.

We do not accept support from governments or political organisations=20
for our campaigning work against human rights abuses, only from=20
individuals like you. Please join today.
https://www.amnesty.org.au/about/membership?utm_source=3Dnewsletter&utm_m=
edium=3Demail&utm_term=3Ddonate+today&utm_content=3D09Jul2008

