f;line-height:1.3;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:5px;margin-right:0;margin=
-left:0;" >Vision 2014: Activist consultation</h2>=20
<p>We're in the process of setting our vision to 2014, looking at the are=
as in which we can make the greatest human rights impact.</p>
<p>We invite all activists and supporters to get involved and have a say =
in the future direction of the organisation. Have a look at <a href=3D"ht=
tp://amnestyinternationalaustralia.cmail2.com/l/457503/86dc4jr/t" style=3D=
"color:#000;" >our proposed vision</a> then let us know your views - we v=
alue your contribution.</p>
<p><a href=3D"http://amnestyinternationalaustralia.cmail2.com/l/457503/86=
dc4jr/i" style=3D"color:#000;" >Fill in our survey</a></p>
